Usage: fix_multi_drivers [-help] [-exclude_net <netName | netNameList>]
                         [-replace_bus_bit] [-report_only]

-help                                    # Prints out the command usage
-exclude_net <netName | netNameList>     # list of nets ((net)+, optional)
-replace_bus_bit                         # This option replace all bus port
                                         # with wrong directions, if any, by
                                         # new scalar ports. If not specified,
                                         # just report without such
                                         # replacement. (bool, optional)
-report_only                             # Report, but not fix, list of all
                                         # ports with wrong directions.
                                         # (bool, optional)